Package: RGIFT
Version: 0.1-6
Encoding: UTF-8
Date: 2023-11-17
Title: Create quizzes in GIFT Format
Author: María José Haro-Delicado, Virgilio Gómez-Rubio and Francisco 
  Parreńo-Torres
Maintainer: Virgilio Gómez-Rubio <virgilio.gomez@uclm.es>
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0)
Suggests: foreign
Description: This package provides some functions to create quizzes
  in the GIFT format. This format is used by several Virtual Learning
  Environments such as Moodle.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://docs.moodle.org/21/en/GIFT_format
